  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/e0e450607218471a201536a70527210a.avif?t=1723824284\" width=646 height=66 /></span><br><br>Exoracer is a fast-paced multiplayer platformer game where you compete for the world record. Play on short and fun levels to get the best time as you can. The game includes more than 300 official and featured levels that you will unlock as you progress in races. You can also play over 80.000 levels made by the community!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/ab83374d920ef709bf480eb7787d95e0.poster.avif?t=1723824284\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/ab83374d920ef709bf480eb7787d95e0.webm?t=1723824284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/ab83374d920ef709bf480eb7787d95e0.mp4?t=1723824284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/04f9037556e5a0b27c47cf6cdff4effb.avif?t=1723824284\" width=646 height=66 /></span><br><br>Compete in short 2-minute races against other players. The player with the best time at the end of the timer wins the race. Climb the ranks and unlock rewards!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/b1f2a08401ee32f3d8b33f27d87fc054.poster.avif?t=1723824284\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/b1f2a08401ee32f3d8b33f27d87fc054.webm?t=1723824284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/b1f2a08401ee32f3d8b33f27d87fc054.mp4?t=1723824284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/afdab3a7dd9a3972ae5d684f774d2ee6.avif?t=1723824284\" width=646 height=66 /></span><br><br>Exoracer comes with an advanced level editor so you can make and share your own levels. The editor includes a visual scripting language to add custom logic to your levels!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/b148211c9f5939827f34b37715f14e26.poster.avif?t=1723824284\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/b148211c9f5939827f34b37715f14e26.webm?t=1723824284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845120/extras/b148211c9f5939827f34b37715f14e26.mp4?t=1723824284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
